%% =====================================================================
%% lgwks — THE ONE DATA MODEL: the State Fabric (whole pipeline)
%% Authority: spec/second-harness/ARCH-two-db-multitenant.md + lgwks_fabric_projection.
%%
%% THE 1 = ONE Source of Record (CausalTape) + MANY cid-keyed, tier-tagged
%% PROJECTIONS joined through one seam (StorageGate.ingest_artifact), read through
%% ONE access locus (lgwks_access.TenantStore, own ⊕ world). NOT one giant table —
%% one tape, many derived/rebuildable views. The relational SQL surface is a
%% COMPILED projection, never the ontology.
%%
%% Status (verified at HEAD): the fabric is BUILT end-to-end (write→read→harden; #152
%% Phases 2–4 + #277 landed PRs #289/#290/#291). lgwks_storage registers
%% 4 projections — VectorProjection(→vector_records), PostingProjection(BM25),
%% FactProjection(+global_facts), RelationalProjection(sources/documents/chunks/
%% vectors/facts/frontier), and GraphFabric(wraps entity_graph; #169 made it the
%% single graph store, replacing per-run graph.db).
%%
%% CONVERGENCE STATUS:
%%   A) [#165 step 3 LANDED, PR #274] lgwks_jarvis.* no longer writes a per-run
%%      research.sqlite island — the JarvisDB writer is retired. The legacy crawler now
%%      persists through GateWriter → StorageGate.ingest_artifact (tape SoR + cid-keyed
%%      embeddings, store-once across runs) and graph_fabric/relational projections. The
%%      gate is keyed on the run NAME, so successive runs accumulate + cross-run-dedup into
%%      ONE store; run_id is provenance (artifact meta + node/edge attrs), never a shard key.
%%      [embed_port.system_graph converged on the tape — #165 step 1, PR #271.]
%%   B) [#165 step 2 + enforcement LANDED, PR #272 + #276] GraphFabric.apply() is live +
%%      entity_graph nodes/edges/chunks carry artifact_cid (tape provenance) + tier (world ⊕
%%      tenant). #276 closed the deferred items: read-side world⊕tenant ENFORCEMENT on graph
%%      reads (scope_tier filters tier=:me OR 'world' OR NULL; gate-scoped) + per-row
%%      artifact_cid back-link from the substrate producer. Graph-read door convergence onto
%%      capability-gated TenantStore [#277 LANDED, PR #291]: TenantStore.over_gate makes the
%%      door projection-generic — graph reads gate on the VERIFIED capability + scope to the
%%      verified principal; scope_tier is now internal behind the door.
%%   C) CONVERGED [#165 LANDED, PR #289]: lgwks_run.py + lgwks_research.py mirror their outputs
%%      (prevector.graph.json/embeddings.jsonl; REPORT.md) onto the tape via the gate (best-
%%      effort, stable corpus gate — no per-run islands). substrate_run stamps every
%%      chunk/fact/vector/media row with tokenization_id + artifact_cid (provenance to the tape
%%      entry). (item 2 lgwks_ingest.py was removed — moot.)
%%   D) Read + harden [#166 PR #290, #167 PR #291 LANDED]: FabricReader.query unifies
%%      lexical+token+graph+vector in one result set; `lgwks state fabric {status,tokenizers,
%%      replay,query}` CLI; CausalTape.verify_chain makes the tape tamper-evident and replay
%%      refuses an inconsistent tape.
%% =====================================================================
